        Artmob is a urban production lab of original collaborative installations and performances (the concept merges Art with the Flash Mob approach).
      %p.project-description
        Are you an urban artist, designer, film-maker, architect or performer? Do you already have a group of collaborators, or are you keen to found one and work together in a multidisciplinary, collaborative experience?
        If so, Artmob is designed for you:
      %p.project-description.point
        go to www.artmob.it
      %p.project-description.point
        create a collaborative project / find one / publish your own in search for further partners
      %p.project-description.point
        submit the project and get 5k€ of funding + the exclusive mentorship of international experts in the field of art and communication
      %p.project-description.point
        activate your project idea in one of the 4 partner cities of Artmob: Alessandria, Asti, Casale Monferrato, Giaveno!
      %p.project-description
        ArtMob is a project funded by the Youth Department of the The Presidency of the Council of Ministers and of the Union of Italian Municipalities, boosted by Fondazione Pistoletto-Città dell’Arte, which involved us – The Doers – as designers and developers of the web platform, as well as ‘digital mentors‘ for the community of artists.
      %p.project-description
        The web platform of ArtMob is the result of the collaboration among us and Paolo, Juan, Caterina, Armona, Margherita – from Città del’Arte – and a larger group of contributors from the network of ArtMob’s partners.
      %p.project-description
        We hope to facilitate the activation of many and interdisciplinary group of artists and we are looking forward to give digital birth to the next project we are cultivating with Paolo & friends from Città dell’Arte!
